                        <p class="subsubheader py-2 me-5" data-scrollreveal="enter bottom over 1s and move 50px after 0.1s">Bonafide members of the University and Constituent Universities may use the library. The undergraduate and graduate students must present their Form 5 to the staff-in-charge at the Circulation Desk for the issuance of library pass.</p>

